Question: The distances from a point $P$ to five of the vertices of a regular octahedron are 3, 7, 8, 9, and 11.  Find the distance from $P$ to the sixth vertex.

[asy]
import three;

size(125);
currentprojection = perspective(6,3,1);

triple A, B, C, D, E, F, P;

A = (1,0,0);
B = (-1,0,0);
C = (0,1,0);
D = (0,-1,0);
E = (0,0,1);
F = (0,0,-1);
P = (1.2,1.5,1);

draw(A--P,red);
draw(B--P,red);
draw(C--P,red);
draw(D--P,red);
draw(E--P,red);
draw(F--P,red);

draw(A--C);
draw(A--D);
draw(A--E);
draw(A--F);
draw(C--E--D--F--cycle);
draw(D--B--C,dashed);
draw(B--C,dashed);
draw(B--D,dashed);
draw(B--E,dashed);
draw(B--F,dashed);

label("$P$", P, NE);
[/asy]
--------------------------------------------------
Generation:

A regular octahedron has six vertices, and the distances from a point inside space to the vertices of an octahedron are equal. This is because the octahedron is symmetric and the distances from any point to the vertices are equal.Distant from point \( P \) to five vertices the distances distances are 3, 7, 8, 9, and 11. Since the distances tetrahedron is symmetric, the distance from \( P \) to the sixth vertex must also be one of the given distances.
</reasoning>
<answer>
\boxed{7}
</answer><|eot_id|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|><|endoftext|>
